'''Haldan''' was the son of [[Haldar]], grandson of [[Haldad]], and nephew to [[Haleth]] herself, who went to [[Brethil]] where she settled her People. Haleth left no heir of her own, and so as grandson of Haldad her father, Haldan took up the [[Lord of Brethil|lordship]] of the [[Men of Brethil]].<ref>{{S|West}}</ref>

